node.text:
@stetsonblaylockfishing starting the final day of the @bass_nation Classic out strong! 💪 How bout that Hard Knocker coming in clutch?!? #bassmasterclassic 
Video credit: @bass_nation

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BOOYAH Bait Co. on August 24, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, outdoors and text that says 'Jluk PERFORMANCE FISHING'.

node.text:
BOOM baby! 💣 @ptd_fishing caught this pig largemouth on an "albino frog" color BOOYAH Pad Crasher! Anyone else trim the legs? 👀 Can help catch short-strikers and make walking the frog easier with a little slack line on each twitch.
#bassfishing

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by BOOYAH Bait Co. on August 20, 2021 tagging @reelintheadventures. May be an image of 1 person and nature.

node.text:
This right here is why you throw the BOOYAH Poppin' Pad Crasher! 🔥 Solid fish @reelintheadventures!! Hope you get to chuck the 🐸 around this weekend too. 👊
#topwater #bassfishing

node.text:
The BOOYAH ToadRunner has a bendable tail 💪 that lets you change the sound, action and speed of the bait. Plop, plop, plop = BOOM! 😎 Move some water and bring 'em to you....
📸: @rawrfishing #bassfishing #topwater

node.text:

#bassfishing #topwater

#topwater #bassfishing

#bassfishing

► 1/2-oz Hard Knocker (Rayburn red)
► 2" Boss Pop (bone shiner)
► XCS100 squarebill (perch)

MSRP of $18.99 and will be at all retail. 👊
